2026-02-21 16:11:49 - INFO - 574 -{"payload": "{\"message\":{\"id\":\"2041dbb0-52bf-4184-a43f-25843b51bda5\",\"source\":\"Travel_Planner\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":3455,\"completion_tokens\":627},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-21T10:41:49.918795Z\",\"content\":\"**The Residency (Karur) \u2013 Approximate Room Rates (2026)**  \\n\\n- **Base nightly rate:**  \\n  - Roughly **US\u202f$60\u202f\u2013\u202f$65** per room.  \\n  - In Indian rupees that translates to **\u20b9\u202f4,800\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f5,500** (exchange rate \u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f80\u202f=\u202f$1).  \\n\\n- **Typical price variations:**  \\n  - **Weekdays (Mon\u2011Wed):** closer to the lower end (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f4,800\u2011\u20b9\u202f5,200).  \\n  - **Peak days (Thu\u2011Fri, holidays):** can rise to the higher end (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f5,300\u2011\u20b9\u202f5,500).  \\n\\n- **Room types shown in the listings:**  \\n  - Standard **Deluxe** or **Superior** rooms \u2013 the rates above apply.  \\n  - Larger **Family** or **Suite** rooms are priced higher (generally **\u20b9\u202f7,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f9,000** per night).  \\n\\n- **Additional charges to expect:**  \\n  - **Roll\u2011away bed:**\u202f\u20b9\u202f1,000 per night (if needed).  \\n  - **City tax / service charge:** usually a small percentage (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f100\u2011\u20b9\u202f200) added at checkout.  \\n\\n- **What\u2019s included in the base rate:**  \\n  - Free Wi\u2011Fi, complimentary self\u2011parking, access to the on\u2011site gym, and daily housekeeping.  \\n\\n- **Best way to lock in the lower rate:**  \\n  - Book **mid\u2011week** (Monday\u2011Wednesday) and look for \u201cnon\u2011refundable\u201d or \u201cpre\u2011pay\u201d options on the booking platform.  \\n\\n**Quick take\u2011away for your 2\u2011day Karur trip**  \\n- Budget **\u20b9\u202f5,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f5,500** per night for a comfortable stay at The Residency.  \\n- Add **\u20b9\u202f1,200\u2011\u20b9\u202f1,500** for taxes/optional roll\u2011away, bringing the total nightly cost to roughly **\u20b9\u202f6,200\u2011\u20b9\u202f7,000**.  \\n\\nThat fits comfortably within your overall \u20b9\u202f50,000 budget while giving you a mid\u2011range hotel experience. Safe travels!\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_bf99fa57-40b5-4a10-b985-8abc3b83752e/bf99fa57-40b5-4a10-b985-8abc3b83752e", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
