ll\u2011away bed:**\u202f\u20b9\u202f1,000 per night (if needed).  \n  - **City tax / service charge:** usually a small percentage (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f100\u2011\u20b9\u202f200) added at checkout.  \n\n- **What\u2019s included in the base rate:**  \n  - Free Wi\u2011Fi, complimentary self\u2011parking, access to the on\u2011site gym, and daily housekeeping.  \n\n- **Best way to lock in the lower rate:**  \n  - Book **mid\u2011week** (Monday\u2011Wednesday) and look for \u201cnon\u2011refundable\u201d or \u201cpre\u2011pay\u201d options on the booking platform.  \n\n**Quick take\u2011away for your 2\u2011day Karur trip**  \n- Budget **\u20b9\u202f5,000\u202f\u2013\u202f\u20b9\u202f5,500** per night for a comfortable stay at The Residency.  \n- Add **\u20b9\u202f1,200\u2011\u20b9\u202f1,500** for taxes/optional roll\u2011away, bringing the total nightly cost to roughly **\u20b9\u202f6,200\u2011\u20b9\u202f7,000**.  \n\nThat fits comfortably within your overall \u20b9\u202f50,000 budget while giving you a mid\u2011range hotel experience. Safe travels!"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-daf0eb17-3688-4b76-b0f5-31f660e9f9a0", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": "APPROVE", "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": null, "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": null, "reasoning": "We need to validate critical realism factors: travel distances, attraction timings, hotel pricing. Already checked distance Chennai-Karur via google_map_tool. Need to check hotel pricing: The Residency rates we fetched via tavily. Need to verify if rates realistic. The user provided summary. We should confirm if price seems realistic. The fetched data shows $60-65 per room, which matches \u20b94800-5500. That seems realistic for mid-range hotel. Also need to check attraction timings if unknown/unusual. The itinerary mentions temple visits, museum, etc. Need to verify timings? Not requested but we could check if any unu